            "id": 6428185,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 莫德納(MRNA-US)大跌5.09%，報51.81美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>莫德納(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRNA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRNA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRNA-US</a>)截至台北時間21日21:33股價下跌2.78美元，報51.81美元，跌幅5.09%，成交量450,057（股），盤中最高價53.95美元、最低價51.68美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.44%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.08%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.05%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.96%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>莫德納(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRNA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRNA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRNA-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+7.72%</li> <li>近 1 月：+6.25%</li> <li>近 3 月：+26.95%</li> <li>近 6 月：+100.4%</li> <li>今年以來：+85.11%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6428185",
